This paper discusses a machine learning problem involving active learning and multi-armed bandit algorithms in a contextual setting. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The paper also involves decision-making and optimization, which could fall under cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) and cs.IT (Information Theory).
